name: Anycubic Predator 0.4 nozzle
machine_end_gcode:
M107 T0
M104 S0
M104 S0 T1
M140 S0
G92 E0
G91
G1 E-1 F300
G1 Z+0.5  F6000
G28 
G90 ;absolute positioning
machine_start_gcode:
G21 ; use millimeters
G90 ; absolute positioning
M82 ; absolute extrusion
M107 T0 ; turn off part cooling fan

M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ; set bed temp
M104 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] T0  ; set nozzle temp
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ; wait for bed
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] T0  ; wait for nozzle

G28 ; home all
G1 X0 Y0 Z5.0 F4000 ; jump to center
G1 X-180 Y0 Z0.4 F2000 ; move to near bed edge
G92 E0 ; reset the extruder

; --- Prime line ---
G1 E5 F300 ; initial prime
G0 X-180.00 Y0.00 Z0.30 E0 F1000
G1 X-179.385 Y-14.864 Z0.30 E3.57042
G1 X-177.545 Y-29.627 Z0.30 E7.14094
G1 X-174.492 Y-44.187 Z0.30 E10.71134
G1 X-170.247 Y-58.446 Z0.30 E14.28195
G1 X-164.839 Y-72.305 Z0.30 E17.85235
G1 X-158.305 Y-85.671 Z0.30 E21.42298
G1 X-150.690 Y-98.451 Z0.30 E24.99339
G1 X-142.045 Y-110.558 Z0.30 E27.56379 ; gradually reducing extrusion
G1 F1500 E26.56379 ; retract 1mm
G1 Z0.5 F3000 ; lift Z slightly
G92 E0 ; reset the extruder
; --- End priming line ---
